data.description: Welcome to your suburban retreat at the end of a cul-de-sac. A quiet neighborhood off the beaten path with only one exit. Walk inside and slip off the day and head to the large back deck. Enjoy the secluded fenced in backyard equipped with large mature trees, raised garden, and an attractive shed for extra storage. The completely fenced in large yard is nice for entertaining, cookouts, or just relaxing. The eat in galley kitchen looks into the family room and kitchen for a nice open layout. There is a room downstairs with French doors that can be used as an extra living room/family room, an office, or a place to study. The entire downstairs area has Brand New Laminate flooring (April 2024). Head upstairs and you will find Brand New Carpet (April 2024) throughout. There are four bedrooms, most very large, plenty of closet space and walk in attic space in the room over the garage.
